1. License Grant
Licensor grants Licensee a non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to access and use the API solely for the purpose of integrating and using the functionality provided by the API within Licensee's applications in accordance with the terms of this Agreement.

2. Seat-Based Licensing
•   Each license purchased is linked to a specific number of developers or seats.
•   A single license allows one developer to use the API. The licensed developer has the right to install and use the API on any number of computers.
•   There are no runtime fees associated with the use of the API.
•   Additional developers must each have their own separate license. A developer without a valid license is not permitted to use the API.

