All rights, title, and interest in and to the API, including all intellectual property rights therein, are and shall remain the property of Licensor. Licensee acquires no rights in the API other than those expressly granted in this Agreement.

6. Confidentiality
Licensee agrees to maintain the confidentiality of any non-public information disclosed by Licensor related to the API and shall not disclose such information to any third party without Licensor's prior written consent.

7. Data Privacy
Licensee shall ensure that any data collected, processed, or stored using the API complies with all applicable data protection and privacy laws. Licensee shall obtain all necessary consents from end-users before collecting any personal data through the API.

8. Termination
Licensor may terminate this Agreement and Licensee's access to the API at any time without notice if Licensee breaches any term of this Agreement. Upon termination, Licensee shall cease all use of the API and delete any data obtained through the API.

