11. Indemnification
Licensee agrees to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless Licensor from and against any and all claims, liabilities, damages, losses, and expenses, including reasonable attorneys' fees, arising out of or in any way connected with Licensee's use of the API or breach of this Agreement.

12. Support
Licensor provides support for the API as part of the license. Support is available Monday through Friday, from 9 AM to 6 PM (French schedules). Licensor will respond to support requests within 24 hours from the submission of the problem.

